text: Väinö Harry Broman (born 29 December 1932) is a Finnish former sports shooter. He competed in the trap event at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1932 births Category:Living people Category:Finnish male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Finland Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Helsinki
